name: What is my TEZ balance?
description:
What?
- This experimental NFT can be used to quickly see your tezos balance. 

How?
- Just open the NFT. 

Requirements?
- You need to sync your wallet on the platform where you are checking the NFT.

Why?
- Just to see if you sold anything :)

No guarantees that this NFT will be working. The NFT is using the API v1 of tzkt.io which can be removed or restricted at any time. Collect it only for fun.
